1953;;The Great Game;;British;;Maurice Elvey;;James Hayter, Thora Hird, Diana Dors;;sports;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Great_Game_(1953_film);;The chairman of a top-flight English football club makes an illegal approach to a rising star of a rival club. This is discovered by the football authorities and the Chairman is ultimately suspended from the game following the ensuing scandal.[3]